ParallelChunk.en:
It is clear once again that the European Parliament and the EU are not only failing to defend democratic rights and grassroots freedom; 

            on the contrary

        , they are restricting them to the point of extinction through a web of reactionary legislative measures and agreements.

To an unacceptable degree, they make the exercising of social rights subject to a 'proportionality principle' which far exceeds lawful restrictions (public order and health, 
          for example
        ) recognised in national laws and ILO conventions.

ParallelChunk.fr:
Ils subordonnent de manière inacceptable l'exercice des droits sociaux à un "principe de proportionnalité" qui va bien au-delà des restrictions légitimes (ordre et santé publics 
          par exemple
        ) reconnues dans les droits nationaux et les conventions de l'OIT.
